dct_title_s: Croatia city graphic 1:20,000. Osijek. Series M903
dct_description_sm: United States. National Imagery and Mapping Agency Alternte title: Osijek. Transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 20 meter contour intervals and spot elevations. Coordinate conversion WGS84 to ED50. "Map information as of 1993." This sheet falls within NL 34-07, 1501, 1:250,000 and 2886 III, M709, 1:50,000. With glossary. In lower righ margin: "WGS 84."
